{"title":"Get gene sets","markdown":{"headingText":"Get gene sets","headingAttr":{"id":"sec-misc","classes":[],"keyvalue":[]},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n## Libraries\n```{r}\nlibrary(dplyr)\nlibrary(tidyverse)\n```\n\n## Assign PrimaryCluster colors\n## Load all TCRs from Alex's scRNA+scTCR analysis\n```{r}\nalex_reactivities <- read.csv(\"../objects/reformatted_RCC_slideseq_parameters_052925.csv\")\n\nalex_reactivities %>%\n  distinct(PrimaryCluster, identity)\n```\n\n## Assign colors\n```{r}\nprimarycluster_fill <- scale_fill_manual(values = c(\"Other/NA\" = \"grey60\", \"Tmem\" = \"#0330F3\", \"Tex\" = \"#931101\", \"TEx\" = \"#FF7F78\", \"TEM\" = \"#0096FE\", \"Treg\" = \"#ff4ff0\", \"TNCM\" = \"#2171B5\", \"unknown\" = \"grey30\"))\nprimarycluster_color <- scale_color_manual(values = c(\"Other/NA\" = \"grey60\", \"Tmem\" = \"#0330F3\", \"Tex\" = \"#931101\", \"TEx\" = \"#FF7F78\", \"TEM\" = \"#0096FE\", \"Treg\" = \"#ff4ff0\", \"TNCM\" = \"#2171B5\", \"unknown\" = \"grey30\"))\n```\n\n## Save colors\n```{r, eval = FALSE}\nsaveRDS(primarycluster_fill, \"../objects/PrimaryCluster_fill.rds\")\nsaveRDS(primarycluster_color, \"../objects/PrimaryCluster_color.rds\")\n```\n\n# Assign Patient colors\n## Assign colors\n```{r}\npatient_fill <- scale_fill_manual(values = c(\"P102TA\" = \"#FF9300\", \"P107TA\" = \"#FF8AD8\", \"P108TA\" = \"#009193\", \"P108TAB\" = \"#009193\", \"P109TB\" = \"#531B93\", \"P110TB\" = \"#941100\", \"P111TA\" = \"#D4FB79\"))\npatient_color <- scale_color_manual(values = c(\"P102TA\" = \"#FF9300\", \"P107TA\" = \"#FF8AD8\", \"P108TA\" = \"#009193\", \"P108TAB\" = \"#009193\", \"P109TB\" = \"#531B93\", \"P110TB\" = \"#941100\", \"P111TA\" = \"#D4FB79\"))\n```\n\n## Save colors\n```{r, eval = FALSE}\nsaveRDS(patient_fill, \"../objects/Patient_fill.rds\")\nsaveRDS(patient_color, \"../objects/Patient_color.rds\")\n```\n\n## Assign area colors\n## Assign colors\n```{r}\narea_color <- scale_color_manual(values = c(\"Boundary\" = \"#ff8f1b\", \"TLS1\" = \"#8A9A5B\", \"TLS2\" = \"#8A9A5B\", \"TLS3\" = \"#8A9A5B\", \"TLS4\" = \"#8A9A5B\", \"Tumor\" = \"#8c6b2d\", \"Granuloma\" = \"#9c5c58\", \"M2\" = \"#9c5c58\", \"Empty\" = \"#eeeeee\"))\narea_fill <- scale_fill_manual(values = c(\"Boundary\" = \"#ff8f1b\", \"TLS1\" = \"#8A9A5B\", \"TLS2\" = \"#8A9A5B\", \"TLS3\" = \"#8A9A5B\", \"TLS4\" = \"#8A9A5B\", \"Tumor\" = \"#8c6b2d\", \"Granuloma\" = \"#9c5c58\", \"M2\" = \"#9c5c58\", \"Empty\" = \"#eeeeee\"))\n```\n\n## Save colors\n```{r, eval = FALSE}\nsaveRDS(area_fill, \"../objects/Area_fill.rds\")\nsaveRDS(area_color, \"../objects/Area_color.rds\")\n```\n\n## Get session info\n```{r}\nsessionInfo()\n```\n\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"knitr"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wra